your shop. It's flagged that way in reports."},{"label":"Cavity Count","value":"For molds: how many cavities (parts made per shot). Used when planning production."},{"label":"Tool Life Expectancy","value":"How many total shots or cycles the tool should last before it needs replacing. Compared against the current shot count."},{"label":"Current Shot Count","value":"Read-only on the detail view. How many shots or cycles the tool has run. As it nears the tool life, the tool is getting close to replacement."},{"label":"Source Job","value":"Read-only link. The job that produced this tool. Click it to open that job."},{"label":"Source Part","value":"Read-only link. The part this tool makes. Click it to open that part."}]},{"heading":"Asset Statuses","items":[{"label":"Active (green)","value":"In service and ready to use. This is where new assets start."},{"label":"Maintenance (yellow)","value":"Down for maintenance right now, planned or not. Tells the team the machine isn't available."},{"label":"Retired (gray)","value":"Taken out of service for good. The record stays for history and depreciation."},{"label":"Out of Service (red)","value":"Broken or otherwise unavailable. Unlike Maintenance, this means an unplanned outage."}]},{"heading":"Asset Types and Icons","items":[{"label":"Machine","value":"Production equipment such as a CNC, lathe, saw, or press."},{"label":"Tooling","value":"Molds, dies, jigs, fixtures, and cutting tools. Adds fields for cavity count, shot count, and customer ownership."},{"label":"Facility","value":"Buildings, HVAC, electrical, and other infrastructure."},{"label":"Vehicle","value":"Delivery trucks, forklifts, and company vehicles."},{"label":"Other","value":"Anything that doesn't fit the categories above."}]},{"heading":"Buttons and Actions","items":[{"label":"Add Asset","value":"Opens the form to add a new asset."},{"label":"Save","value":"Creates or updates the asset. Grayed out while the form has a problem or a save is already running."},{"label":"Cancel","value":"Closes the form without saving."},{"label":"Edit (detail panel)","value":"Reopens the form already filled in with the asset's current values."},{"label":"Set Status buttons (detail)","value":"Quick buttons on the detail panel to switch an asset to Active, Maintenance, Retired, or Out of Service."},{"label":"Row click","value":"Opens the asset, showing all its fields, tooling details, barcode, and maintenance history."}]},{"heading":"Machine Operating Hours","items":[{"label":"Current Hours (table + detail)","value":"The asset's running total of operating hours. Shown in the Current Hours column (a dash when it's zero) and on the detail panel. Read-only on both screens."},{"label":"How hours are updated","value":"Hours come from the machine-hours action, not by typing them on the detail panel. They feed tool-life and maintenance-interval tracking. There's no free-text hours box on the detail panel today."},{"label":"Why hours matter","value":"Rising hours are what move usage-based maintenance intervals and, for tooling, tool-life along. Keep them current so scheduled maintenance comes due on time."}]},{"heading":"Validation Rules","items":[{"label":"Name","value":"Required. Can't be left blank."},{"label":"Type","value":"Required. Pick one of the five types."},{"label":"Acquisition Cost","value":"Optional, but if you enter it, it must be zero or more and no higher than one billion. Anything outside that blocks Save."},{"label":"All other fields","value":"Optional, with no special length or format rules."},{"label":"When Save is grayed out","value":"When something's missing or wrong, the marker next to Save tells you which fields need attention."}]},{"heading":"Table Columns","items":[{"label":"Icon","value":"The asset type's icon. Can't be sorted by."},{"label":"Name","value":"The asset's name. Sortable."},{"label":"Asset Type","value":"Machine, Tooling, Facility, Vehicle, or Other. Sortable and filterable."},{"label":"Location","value":"Where the asset sits. Sortable."},{"label":"Manufacturer","value":"Who made the equipment. Sortable."},{"label":"Status","value":"A colored label: Active (green), Maintenance (yellow), Retired (gray), Out of Service (red). Sortable."},{"label":"Current Hours","value":"The asset's tracked operating hours. Sortable."}]}]}"""
